query.result:
**English:**

143 Pistoia will grow thin before the Neri;
144 then Florence will renew its people and customs.

145 Mars draws vapors from the Val di Magra
146 which is wrapped in stormy clouds;
147 and with a tempestuous and bitter storm

148 it will be fought over Campo Piceno;
149 from which it will suddenly break the mist,
150 so that every White will be wounded by it.

**Cornish:**

